People have been speaking about Seibra bringing visitor to Agartha. Too bad Catherine can't speak Agarthian. "Catherine" and "Katarmaga" almost same name. Seibra must have believed was funny! I have not travelled out in long time, think Terrans changed too much. And... *is interrupted*
C: Slow down a moment! I guess this is Agartha? Why do I look like Seibra? What happened to Seibra? I have questions! I'm scared...
K: It's easier when you have rest. Be my friend and maybe I can help shop new body. Helps people not confuse you with Seibra again! If troubles are not fixed, get pet. Pet always likes you.

