K: "Calm down, this is not the physical world anymore! Have you felt hunger or a need for a toilet break since you arrived in Agartha?"
C: "Wait, what? You're right, I would have felt my stomach rumble after waking up. So what you are saying is that these bodies of ours are like... Skins in a videogame or something?"
